Package org.cibseven.bpm.engine.cdi

Class ProcessVariables

java.lang.Object
org.cibseven.bpm.engine.cdi.ProcessVariables
public class ProcessVariables extends Object
Allows to access the process variables of a managed process instance. A process instance can be managed, using the BusinessProcess-bean.
Author:
Daniel Meyer
